ProjetSae502/
├── playbooks/
│   ├── execplaybooks.yml
│   ├── deploy_security_onion.yml
│   ├── deploy_ftp.yml
│   ├── deploy_mailu.yml
│   ├── configure_ssl_ftp.yml
│   └── configure_alerting.yml
└── inventaire/
    └── hosts.ini



cette commande permet de créer l'arborescence: 

mkdir -p ProjetSae502/{playbooks,inventaire} && \
touch ProjetSae502/playbooks/{execplaybooks.yml,deploy_security_onion.yml,deploy_ftp.yml,deploy_mailu.yml,configure_ssl_ftp.yml,configure_alerting.yml} && \
touch ProjetSae502/inventaire/hosts.ini
